      BUSINESS PROBLEM STATEMENT:

      BUSINESS PROBLEM STATEMENT:

      In [ ]:
      xxxxxxxxxx
       
      Aerofit provides wide range of fitness products including treadmills.The market research team wants to find out target audience
      for each type of treadmill offered by the company and their characteristics in order to  provide a better recommendation of the 
      treadmills to the new customers.These can be done by doing univariate and bivariate analysis adding data visualisation to it.
      Creating a customer profile for each treadmill and computing conditional and marginal probabilities can help in finding out the 
      characteristics of cutomers.
